feat(playground): build typography system + spacing editor

- Google Fonts picker with 31 curated fonts (sans, serif, mono)
- Three font slots: Display, Body, Mono with searchable dropdown
- Local font upload via @font-face + createObjectURL
- Type scale editor: base size slider + 8 ratio presets + live preview
- Line height slider (1.0-2.0)
- Spacing scale editor: base unit slider with visual bar preview
- Token editor reorganized into 5 collapsible sections
- Export JSON updated to include all new variables

